    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced subframe, addressing the platform's critical areas. The chassis remains sharp thanks to Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized. While showing light interior patina, the drivetrain delivers linear power and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car with a factory limited-slip differential, ready for spirited canyon runs.",
