    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! If you're looking for a reliable car that still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel, you've gotta come check this one out. Let's get you in the driver's seat!",
