    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This chassis has undergone essential subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high torque loads. The VANOS variable valve timing system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and rattle kits for peak volumetric efficiency. It features the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with a short-throw shifter, delivering power through a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry is sharpened by Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing adjustable compression and rebound. While the aesthetic reflects its mileage, the drivetrain is synchronized perfectly, offering the linear power delivery and metallic rasp synonymous with BMW M's peak atmospheric era.",
